page.title: 09A school childs day
page.content: I get up at about half past six. I get dressed and washed before breakfast. Whilst I am making my breakfast I also make my little brother and sisters breakfast I also get the dogs ready. After we have our breakfast my sister and I get our school bags ready. After that I take the dog a walk around our feild. The school car comes to pick us up. We arrive at school about 8.40am. There are two school runs one up the East end and one up the West end of the island. When we get to school we do our work until ten forty. Then after playtime we have our lunch at 12:30 and another playtime at 2:30. We go home at 3:30.
